Introduction

Wooyeon is a South Korean singer and Actress signed with H Music Entertainment. Wooyeon is the Lead Vocalist & Visual of the girl group WOOAH (formerly known as woo!ah!).

She made her debut as a member of WOOAH on May 15, 2020, with the group's first single album "Exclamation". That same year, she also made her debut as an actress with the drama “My YouTube Diary Season 2.” She continued her acting career with roles in the dramas "Ongoing Loved One"(2022), “Revenge of Others”(2022) and "Snap and Spark"(2023).

In 2023, she participated in the Mnet survival show "Queendom Puzzle", where she was eliminated after ranking 9th.
